                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_020",
                    "text": "%Angel%: Hey, that was some clever thinking, combining the damaged codes from different ships.",
                    "textb": "%Angel%: Well, well, well. I'd have bet my wings the X-Men and The Brotherhood would never work together. Guess I was wrong.",
                    "response": {
                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                        "line": {
                            "text": "%PLAYER%: It was nothing, really. What have you been up to?",
                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: Yeah, I guess you were. Xavier said you had information for us.",
                            "response": {
                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                "line": {
                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_012",
                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_022",
                                    "text": "%Angel%: Professor Xavier sent me to scout for possible entrances to Genosha. I found one, but you aren't going to like the location.",
                                    "textb": "%Angel%: The Professor sent me to scout Genosha for possible entrances. I found one, but it's in a real bad place.",
                                    "response": {
                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                        "line": {
                                            "text": "%PLAYER%: Where is it?",
                                            "textb": "%PLAYER%: Where's that?",
                                            "response": {
                                                "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                "line": {
                                                    "soundtoplay": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_014",
                                                    "soundtoplayb": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_024",
                                                    "text": "%Angel%: Deep in the Cerci tunnels that border the Dead Zone. The bugs have uncovered a door that was buried during an earthquake. Your security code should open it.",
                                                    "textb": "%Angel%: Down in the Cerci tunnels. The bugs have dug so deep they uncovered a door that had been buried by an earthquake. That security code you've got should unlock it.",
                                                    "response": {
                                                        "text": "%BLANK%",
                                                        "line": {
                                                            "soundtoplay": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_015",
                                                            "soundtoplayb": "voice/angel/1_sanctuary1_125_025",
                                                            "text": "%Angel%: Use the mission computer if you want a full briefing.",
                                                            "textb": "%Angel%: If you need a full briefing, use the mission computer by Professor Xavier.",
                                                            "response": {
